==Public Meetings== ===Things to Note=== *Meetings will be the second and fourth Thursday of the month. *First meeting of 2010 will be January 14, 2010. *Gangplank has free Wifi (WOOHOO!!) ===Gangplank=== [http://www.gangplankhq.com www.gangplankhq.com] ===Location=== [http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&source=s_q&hl=en&geocode=&q=gangplank,+chandler+,az&sll=37.0625,-95.677068&sspn=48.956293,79.013672&ie=UTF8&hq=gangplank,&hnear=Chandler,+AZ&z=13&iwloc=A&cid=8705411617655272523 325 East Elliot Rd. Suite 34 Chandler, AZ 85225]
(On the south side of Elliot between Arizona Ave and McQueen Road.) ==Social== We’re looking to venture out to cool places we hear about (in a totally informal way) one of the other Thursdays of the month. (probably going to be the 3rd one). First up, I believe, is going to be Organ Stop Pizza. Feel free to bring the fam’, girlfriend/boyfriend, bestfriend/nemesis… whatever! ==Project Nights== # Sept 17th 2009: Potato Cannons
